name: The Nexus Point #1
description:
Three heroes plucked from three periods of time, brought together at a moment in time known as The Nexus Point to save the world from the end of days...

This edition comes signed and with a sketch by the author Stewart Cook.

Books will ship from April 1st 2012.

name: Revenge #1
description:
"A non-stop thrill ride of exceptional man-made awesome"

They pushed and pushedâ€¦ now he's pushing back. HARD!

A mysterious vigilante known only as 'M' begins a spree of bloody retribution across the city and Detective Clint Martins is left playing catch-up to his vigilante spree.

Revenge is illustrated by Stewart Cook with two colour interiors and a stunning cover by Joel van der Knaap.

Revenge is written by Anthony Sherratt and Stewart Cook.

name: Dave: Zombie Hunter. Book One.
description:
The dead have begun to rise from the grave and only one man can stop this catastrophic (nay, awesome!) event from destroying the world... He is Dave... Dave: Zombie Hunter!!

Along with his best mate Chuck and his nymphomaniac girlfriend Vera, Dave sets off on a wild, song filled ride of dark mayhem and violence (and even darker comedy...)

Dave: Zombie Hunter is written by Stewart Cook and Illustrated by Tim Ide.

For more Dave (and interior art) check out http://davezombiehunter.tumblr.com/
